OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1777903627
OL,3,CBrothers set to smash #1m dementia
OL,4,Cfundraising goal during marathon
OL,5,Cchallenge
OL,7,FTwo brothers taking part in a marathon
OL,8,Fchallenge for dementia research are
OL,9,Fset to smash a #1 million fundraising
OL,10,Ftarget as they travel across Ireland.
OL,12,FJordan and Cian Adams have been
OL,13,Fdiagnosed with a rare gene which
OL,14,Fcauses frontotemporal dementia (FTD),
OL,15,Fwhich means they have a high chance of
OL,16,Fdeveloping dementia in their 40s.
OL,18,FTheir mother Geraldine died at the age
OL,19,Fof 52 after developing FTD.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1777903627
OL,3,CBrothers set to smash #1m dementia
OL,4,Cfundraising goal during marathon
OL,5,Cchallenge
OL,7,FJordan, 30, is running 33 marathons in
OL,8,F33 days to raise funds and awareness
OL,9,Fof dementia, with support from physio
OL,10,Fbrother Cian, 25.
OL,12,FThe so-called FTD Brothers, from
OL,13,FRedditch, Worcestershire, had set a
OL,14,Ftarget of raising #1 million before
OL,15,Fthey develop symptoms.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1777903627
OL,3,CBrothers set to smash #1m dementia
OL,4,Cfundraising goal during marathon
OL,5,Cchallenge
OL,7,FJordan began by running the London
OL,8,FMarathon on April 26 while carrying a
OL,9,F25kg fridge on his back, before
OL,10,Ftravelling to Ireland to run a
OL,11,Fmarathon a day in each of the 32
OL,12,Fcounties across the island.
OL,14,FThe odyssey included competing in the
OL,15,FBelfast Marathon on Sunday and will
OL,16,Fconclude in Dublin on May 28.
OL,18,FOn Monday, hundreds came out to
OL,19,Fsupport the brothers as they set off
OL,20,Ffor their latest run in Dundalk, Co
OL,21,FLouth.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1777903627
OL,3,CBrothers set to smash #1m dementia
OL,4,Cfundraising goal during marathon
OL,5,Cchallenge
OL,7,FCian told the Press Association: "It
OL,8,Fis really rare but familial
OL,9,Ffrontotemporal dementia runs in our
OL,10,Ffamily.
OL,12,F"That accounts for less than 1% of
OL,13,Fdementias.
OL,15,F"Mum was one of 13 cousins, and eight
OL,16,Fout of the 13 had dementia in their
OL,17,F40s.
OL,19,F"Myself and my brother Jordan have
OL,20,Fbeen tested and we know that we carry
OL,21,Fthe mutation that causes that FTD."
OL,26,@oD@bOUtD@AOUwD@AOU{D@AOU}D@cO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1777903627
OL,3,CBrothers set to smash #1m dementia
OL,4,Cfundraising goal during marathon
OL,5,Cchallenge
OL,7,FJordan said: "I was 15 when mum was
OL,8,Fdiagnosed. Mum went from being this
OL,9,Fvivacious, bubbly, life and soul
OL,10,Fcharacter, she had this amazing gift
OL,11,Fof leaving her presence in every year.
OL,12,FShe was a beautiful person inside and
OL,13,Fout.
OL,26,@oD@NOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1777903627
OL,3,CBrothers set to smash #1m dementia
OL,4,Cfundraising goal during marathon
OL,5,Cchallenge
OL,7,F"We noticed small but significant
OL,8,Fchanges around 2008/09 when mum became
OL,9,Fmore socially withdrawn, she wasn't
OL,10,Fherself, and alongside that were the
OL,11,Fissues with memory and the basic,
OL,12,Fsimple cognitive tasks like driving us
OL,13,Fto school in the morning became
OL,14,Fdifficult for her.
OL,16,F"My dad went on a journey to get
OL,17,Fanswers and it took him two years to
OL,18,Feventually get the diagnosis.
OL,20,F"She died at the age of 52.
OL,26,@oD@AOUxD@AOU|D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1777903627
OL,3,CBrothers set to smash #1m dementia
OL,4,Cfundraising goal during marathon
OL,5,Cchallenge
OL,7,F"She was a shell of the human being
OL,8,Fshe had been, and it was incredibly
OL,9,Fcruel to watch."
OL,11,FJordan added: "Just two years later,
OL,12,Fin 2018, my genetic consultant told me
OL,13,FI am a carrier of the mutation. That
OL,14,Fgives me a 99.9% chance of getting FTD.
OL,16,F"Since then I have tried to use my
OL,17,Fdiagnosis as a licence to live.
OL,19,F"We don't have a choice with the cards
OL,20,Fyou get dealt in life, but you have a
OL,21,Fchoice at how you play your hand.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@PO]sD@OOUxD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1777903627
OL,3,CBrothers set to smash #1m dementia
OL,4,Cfundraising goal during marathon
OL,5,Cchallenge
OL,7,F"Five years later Cian was given the
OL,8,Fdiagnosis at the age of 23. Overnight
OL,9,Fthe FTD Brothers were born."
OL,11,FThe brothers have raised hundreds of
OL,12,Fthousands of pounds for charity over
OL,13,Fthe past eight years, but said their
OL,14,Ffundraising efforts and recognition
OL,15,Fhave taken off since they began their
OL,16,Flatest challenge.
OL,18,FJordan said: "We have come back to the
OL,19,Fplace my mum called home here in
OL,20,FIreland and we have been received like
OL,21,Fwe could never have expected.
OL,26,@oD@AOUqD@\O]zD@NOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G8/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44209
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1777903627
OL,3,CBrothers set to smash #1m dementia
OL,4,Cfundraising goal during marathon
OL,5,Cchallenge
OL,7,F"The Irish people have got behind us
OL,8,Fso incredibly.
OL,10,F"I think we are going to need some
OL,11,Fcrowd control by the time we get to
OL,12,FDublin because it is getting a bit
OL,13,Fcrazy."
OL,15,FCian said: "The public reaction has
OL,16,Fbeen absolutely mind-blowing,
OL,17,Funbelievable. We didn't expect the
OL,18,Flevel of support we would get.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@AOUuD@GO]wD@LOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G9/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44210
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1777903627
OL,3,CBrothers set to smash #1m dementia
OL,4,Cfundraising goal during marathon
OL,5,Cchallenge
OL,7,F"It takes Jordan about 10 minutes to
OL,8,Fget anywhere because he is like the
OL,9,Fselfie king now.
OL,11,F"We are grateful to the Irish people
OL,12,Ffor getting behind two English lads."
OL,14,FJordan has battled aches and pains and
OL,15,Fblisters, but said the support he had
OL,16,Freceived made it hard to feel tired.
OL,18,FHe said: "It is motivation to get
OL,19,Fthrough each day.
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@AOUtD@eO]zD@JOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G10/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44211
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1777903627
OL,3,CBrothers set to smash #1m dementia
OL,4,Cfundraising goal during marathon
OL,5,Cchallenge
OL,7,F"I have got another 25 marathons to
OL,8,Frun, we've got a long way to go.
OL,10,F"We're just taking it one day a time.
OL,11,FWe'll just continue building momentum
OL,12,Fand hopefully the body can make it in
OL,13,Fone piece."
OL,15,FThe brothers' "lifetime goal" of
OL,16,Fraising #1 million was surpassed last
OL,17,Fweek, and they are on track of pass #1
OL,18,Fmillion during their London Marathon
OL,19,Fand Irish challenge.
OL,26,@oD@AOUrD@AOUuD@KO]wD@OOUwD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G11/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44212
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1777903627
OL,3,CBrothers set to smash #1m dementia
OL,4,Cfundraising goal during marathon
OL,5,Cchallenge
OL,7,FCian said: "It feels like the whole of
OL,8,FIreland is behind us now and people
OL,9,Fall over the globe."
OL,11,FJordan added: "It has gone beyond the
OL,12,Ffundraising goal, it is the millions
OL,13,Fof people we have inspired around the
OL,14,Fworld.
OL,16,F"To have that sort of impact all over
OL,17,Fthe world is even more important than
OL,18,Fraising a million pounds.
OL,26,@oD@LOUqD@TO]sD@OOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G12/14
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,443,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44213
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F442A1777903627
OL,3,CBrothers set to smash #1m dementia
OL,4,Cfundraising goal during marathon
OL,5,Cchallenge
OL,7,F"There are so many families all over
OL,8,Fthe world who suffer in silence, who
OL,9,Fhave lived through dementia and felt
OL,10,Fthat heartbreak and devastation.
OL,12,F"We finally feel like we are giving a
OL,13,Fvoice to those families, they are
OL,14,Fbeing heard and now we have to use
OL,15,Fthis to create real change."
OL,17,FCian joked that his brother cannot
OL,18,Fhave a Guinness to celebrate the
OL,19,Ffundraising landmark as he's got
OL,20,Fanother 25 marathons to run.
OL,26,@oD@AOUtD@AOUwD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G13/14
